		(property "Description" "USB-C 5V input front-end. Includes USB-C receptacle, USBLC6-2SC6 ESD protection on USB_DP/USB_DM, and 22uF bulk cap across 5V_OUT and GND. Sized for 3A continuous draw. CC1/CC2 are pulled to the receptacle's CC pins; for sink-only operation tie 5.1k to GND on each (handled at the block-instance level if requested)."
			(at 0 0 0)
			(effects
