				)
				(hide yes)
			)
		)
		(property "Description" "ESP32-WROOM-32 module. VCC = 3.3V (350mA peak during WiFi TX). EN has a 10k pull-up + 0.1uF cap. GPIO0/GPIO2/GPIO12/GPIO15 are strapping pins — leave floating during boot or use the dedicated programming circuit. On-board CP2102 USB-UART brings USB_DP/USB_DM in and exposes serial via GPIO1_TX/GPIO3_RX. BOOT button between GPIO0 and GND. 10uF + 100nF decoupling on VCC."
			(at 266.7 76.2 0)
			(effects
				(font
					(size 1.27 1.27)
				)
				(hide yes)
			)
